{"tid":2365329,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手] RE :０選擇硬件砌機","createTime":"2021-01-13T15:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:49.000Z","uid":78143,"like":14,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c341567a6061b0ab0537e1b02c2ec639db08ff","tid":2365329,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"0. 前言<br />\n（驚悶可以唔睇）<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：本人對砌機只有入門級嘅知識，如果有錯請各位巴打細力HI<br />\n<br />\n一個專為砌機新手而設嘅post，並唔會講得太深入，各位喺硬件台PO開既巴打驚悶親可以出返去了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 基本電腦硬件介紹<br />\n<br />\n想試下由零開始自己揀硬件砌機？又或者想度條心水list叫人幫你砌？但係又唔知道硬件之間配唔配合得到？？（砌唔入，開唔到機）<br />\n無問題，而家一一為你解開心底中既疑問！<br />\n要詳細資料，可以自行GOOGLE<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果只係要用得到，一部電腦最基本既構成最有5款硬件！！無錯只係5款！！<br />\n佢地就係<br />\n<br />\n1. 老母板/底板/主機板(Motherboard/Mainboard)<br />\n2. 處理器（CPU/U）<br />\n可以去下面兩間廠商查詢<br />\nINTEL<br />\n<a href=\"https://ark.intel.com/content/www/tw/zh/ark.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fark.intel.com%2Fcontent%2Fwww%2Ftw%2Fzh%2Fark.html&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuDbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=046999a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ark.intel.com/content/www/tw/zh/ark.html</a><br />\n<br />\nAMD<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amd.com/zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amd.com%2Fzh-hant&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuDbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=a5f7211e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amd.com/zh-hant</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 記憶體(Ram/Memory) 大陸叫內存<br />\n4. 火牛(電源供應器/Power Supply/PSU)<br />\n5. 儲存裝置（如3.5&quot;/2.5&quot;Harddisk / SATS/NVME SSD/甚至係USB）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集齊依5樣野，理論上你部機就可以正常開機了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n1. 老母板/底板/主機板(Motherboard/Mainboard)<br />\n<br />\nINTEL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bO9XfWD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbO9XfWD.jpg&h=8e101fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAMD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5Z5G5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5Z5G5g.png&h=bc0f33eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 處理器（CPU/U）<br />\n<br />\nINTEL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2swBBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2swBBL.jpg&h=7ef9c5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAMD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Evh78KW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvh78KW.png&h=a02767a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 記憶體(Ram/Memory)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgGkZvg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgGkZvg.jpg&h=9471cb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 火牛(電源供應器/Power Supply/PSU)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51dSeDpY2jL._AC_SY400_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51dSeDpY2jL._AC_SY400_.jpg&h=1f0c6076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 儲存裝置<br />\n<br />\nHDD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bvvGKPF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbvvGKPF.jpg&h=ede20236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSATA SSD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kajomCQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkajomCQ.png&h=6360ae14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNVME SSD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBX3OBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBX3OBB.jpg&h=d3897eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁上面就係一部電腦既基本構成啦，但都只係僅僅開到機... 未必代表可以足夠你正常使用架！<br />\nINTEL CPU要用INTEL 主機板<br />\nAMD CPU要用AMD主機板<br />\n咁普遍黎講你可能仲需要以下既硬件...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. Cpu散熱器(一般黎講買cpu會送埋，除非係可超頻版)<br />\n7. 機箱（Case/Chassis）<br />\n8. 顯示咭（Graphics Card/Display Card/ GPU）<br />\n注意 : <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9Li1671.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Li1671.gif&h=eba733a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. CPU散熱器<br />\n<br />\n風冷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/whu0ZM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwhu0ZM1.jpg&h=d2e3b8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水冷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFGntFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFGntFk.png&h=94e19bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 機箱（Case/Chassis）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHv8PLX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHv8PLX.png&h=997c0f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 顯示咭（Graphics Card/Display Card/ GPU）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0evV5EZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0evV5EZ.jpg&h=68f14a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有更多更多唔太常被用到既硬件如wifi咭，藍芽咭，Capture Card<br />\n<br />\n又或者係正常唔會有嘅嘢<br />\n如機箱風扇，RGB燈條，顯示咭千斤頂，SLI/nvlink橋等等, 依度就唔提了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致上就係咁多喇！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家度完條list，想check下有無嘢執漏既可以睇一次提示<br />\n<br />\nCPU 板 Ram SSD Harddisk 機箱 火牛 顯示咭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁其中SSD同Harddisk可以只有其中一個<br />\n<br />\n如果唔洗打機同CPU有IGPU<br />\n<br />\n顯示咭亦唔一定需要買<br />\n<br />\n要買唔送Cooler既CPU的話，就留意要另外買返喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果睇完我嘅提示都執漏件嘅就請正柒頭啦"},{"pid":"a80deba9b347d9e2db53d34c9d24d905c3b0c9e4","tid":2365329,"uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"38b8261a06a0b14f7f1a6cee0fc39c8d7be50385","tid":2365329,"uid":13541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T21:05:19.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"780b501c97f1671331062fbf6e9d370b7a1e17dc","tid":2365329,"uid":213607,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T21:21:32.000Z","msg":"洗撚你講咩 求其上個砌機網塞齊part都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\